The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
May 04, 2011

 



Statement on the Visit of Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu




On May 20, the President will host Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu for a meeting at the White House.Â  The leaders look forward to discussing the full range of issues of mutual interest to the United States and Israel.
